{"word":"μετανοέω","slug":"μετανοέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μετανοέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μετά\">μετά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νοέω\">νοέω</a></el>] ‘have a serious change of mind and heart about a previous point of view or course of behavior’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ esp.\">esp.</a> in the face of extraordinary developments <b>repent <a href='B:470 3:2'>Mt 3:2</a>; <a href='B:470 11:20'>11:20</a>; <a href='B:470 12:41'>12:41</a>; <a href='B:480 1:15'>Mk 1:15</a>; <a href='B:490 10:13'>Lk 10:13</a>; <a href='B:490 11:32'>11:32</a>; <a href='B:490 13:3'>13:3</a>, <a href='B:490 13:5'>5</a>; <a href='B:490 16:30'>16:30</a>; <a href='B:510 2:38'>Ac 2:38</a>; <a href='B:510 8:22'>8:22</a>; <a href='B:510 17:30'>17:30</a>; <a href='B:540 12:21'>2 Cor 12:21</a>; <a href='B:730 2:5'>Rv 2:5</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Rv. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μεταμορφόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μετάνοια\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}